comments:
Renamed 11.10.1976 to become the parish of Holmes Chapel. See 
    also Table 2, note (a).

Unparished area which until 1.4.1974 formed the parish of Congleton. Abolished 1.11.1980 to become the parish of Congleton. 
    See also Table 2, note (b).

Created 1.11.1980 from the Congleton unparished area. See also 
    Table 2, note (f).

Renamed 18.10.1984 to become the parish of Crewe Green. See also 
    Table 2, note (a).

Unparished area which until 1.4.1974 formed the parish of Monks 
    Coppenhall and the borough of Crewe. See also Table 2, notes (a) and 
    (f).

Created 18.10.1984 by renaming the parish of Crewe. See also Table 
    2, note (f).

Created 11.10.1976 by renaming the parish of Church Hulme. See 
    also Table 2, note (f).

Abolished 1.4.1990 and added to the parish of Wrenbury cum 
    Frith. See also Table 2, note (a).
